name: The Golden Ticket by Humble Holders

metadata.name: Golden Ticket by Humble Holders
metadata.description: The Humble Holders is an exclusive collaborative community consisting of Web3 patrons & NFT enthusiasts. Every golden ticket represents a pass granting the Holder a lifetime access to our giveaways, alpha calls and future perks. Our vision is building a project that is held to a high standard, acknowledged within the NFT space and constantly providing benefits for our Holders and Partners, as well as building for the greater good of web3!
